than anywhere on Earth, except Rwanda.

00:05:21.770 --> 00:05:25.310
And giant metal needles do tend to attract
lightning strikes!

00:05:25.310 --> 00:05:28.220
But NASA prepares for this, but what if it
happens in flight?

00:05:28.220 --> 00:05:29.610
That would actually be really bad.

00:05:29.610 --> 00:05:35.150
So, they constantly gather weather data and
if one thing is off, they either wait or they

00:05:35.150 --> 00:05:37.680
scrub the launch for another better day.

